<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Anatoliy Yurkin] </F>
  [Text] Moscow June 27 TASS -- An officer was killed and two 
soldiers wounded in an overnight attack on the guarding unit of 
a tank regiment deployed in the Russian Baltic enclave of 
Kaliningrad. 
  TASS learned from the press service of the Russian Ground 
forces on Monday that the officer was in command of the guards 
