<F P=106> [POSTFACTUM report: "Russian Federation Finance Ministry </F>
Proposes Special Tax To Combat Crime"] 
  [Text] The Russian Federation Finance Ministry has 
forwarded to the government and the Security Council a proposal 
to introduce a special personal income tax to finance the 
federal crime fighting program. The proposed maximum rate of 
the tax is 3 percent. It has been suggested not to tax 
citizens' monthly incomes below 70,000 rubles. 

