conduct a rally in the Kusarskiy Region centre. An employee of 
Azerbaijan's Ministry of Internal Affairs, Fatulla Guseynov, 
told TURAN that the Lezghin community did not inform the 
authorities about their intention to conduct rally in the region 
centre. 

