<H3> <TI>   Russian Border Patrol Fired on From Afghan Territory </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Russian Border Patrol Fired on From Afghan Territory </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2806075694 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0737 GMT 28 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2806075694 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by ITAR-TASS correspondent Galina Gridneva] </F>
  [Text] Dushanbe 28 June TASS -- A border patrol in one of 
the sectors of the Moskovskiy border guarding detachments was 
fired upon from automatic weapons from Afghan territory on 
Monday night, sources at the department of Russian border troops 
in Tajikistan told ITAR-TASS on Tuesday [28 June]. 
  Fire was intensive enough, but, luckily, none of border 
guards was hurt. The border guards did not return the fire, the 
sources said. 
  The situation in the other sectors of the Tajik-Afghan 
border 
remains rather complex but is controlled by Russian border 
guards. 

</TEXT>

