<F P=100> Tajikistan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Concept of Agricultural Development To Be Revised </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Concept of Agricultural Development To Be Revised </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2706150294 Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network in Tajik 1200 
GMT 27 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2706150294 </F>
<F P=104>  Dushanbe Radio Tajikistan Network </F>
<F P=105>  Tajik </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A meeting took place in the Council of Ministers of 
the Republic, under the chairmanship of Abdulmadjid Samadov 
today. 
  The issue relating to revising the concept of development of 
agriculture of the Republic was discussed in the meeting. The 
heads of the relevant ministries and departments and prominent 
scientists of the Tajik Academy of Sciences attended the 
meeting. It was pointed out in the meeting that the present 
concept of development of agriculture should be revised in the 
conditions of the present-day economic crisis of Tajikistan. 
  The absence of foreign loans makes the farmers rely only on 
the use of home resources. [words indistinct] With the purpose 
of revising the concept of development of agriculture of the 
Republic, a working group has been established out of the 
scientists of the country's Academy of Sciences and prominent 
agricultural experts. 

</TEXT>

