<H3> <TI>   Government Passes Program on 1994-97 Activity </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Government Passes Program on 1994-97 Activity </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2706192294 Chisinau BASAPRESS in English 2228 GMT 23 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU2706192294 </F>
<F P=104>  Chisinau BASAPRESS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Chisinau, BASAPRES, 23/06/1994 -- Today, the 
Moldovan Parliament passed (67 votes, against 12) the Program on 
Governmental activity for 1994-97. The opposition factions 
comprising the People's Christian Democratic Front Alliance and 
Peasants and Intellectuals Block voted against. Premier Andrei 
Sangheli stated during the parliamentary session that the main 
strategic objective of the Program is Moldova's economic 
stabilization in 1994-95, the accomplishment of reform on a 
large scale, and the assurance of economic growth that would 
better people's welfare in 1996-97. 

</TEXT>

