<H3> <TI>   Smugglers Caught Trying To Sell Radioactive Substance </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Smugglers Caught Trying To Sell Radioactive Substance </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2806055594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0500 GMT 
28 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2806055594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] According to information in the RABOCHAYA TRIBUNA a 
criminal group which tried to sell a container of radioactive 
substances exported from Russia for $20,000 has been detained by 
the police in Moldova. An expert investigation showed that the 
factory-made package, which was confiscated, contained 
gamma-cobalt-60. In spite of the fact that it had been 
hermetically sealed, the experts discovered a small leak of the 
radioactive substance. 

</TEXT>

