<DOCNO> FBIS4-41789 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drsov124_s_94003" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-SOV-94-124 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  27 Jun 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> Georgia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Shevardnadze Makes Changes in Defense Ministry </TI></H3>
