percent; Kuchma, 20.95 percent; Lanovyy, 18.9 percent; Moroz, 
21.04 percent; Plyushch, 1.7 percent; and Petro Talanchuk, 0.61 
percent. 
  Lugansk oblast: Babych, 1.82 percent; Kravchuk, 9.7 percent; 
Kuchma, 53.61 percent; Lanovyy, 4.53 percent; Moroz, 25.43 
percent; Plyushch, 0.74 percent; and Talanchuk, 0.41 percent. 
  Lvov oblast: Babych, 0.04 percent; Kravchuk, 89.34 percent; 
Kuchma, 3.55 percent; Lanovyy, 1.64 percent; Moroz, 1.21 
percent; Plyushch, 0.48 percent; and Talanchuk 0.01 percent. 
  Nikolayev oblast: Babych, 2.72 percent; Kravchuk, 37.14 
percent; Kuchma 33.37 percent; Lanovyy, 8.84 percent; Moroz 12.6 
percent; Plyushch, 1.08 percent; and Talanchuk, 0.6 percent. 
  Cherkassy oblast: Babych, 2.42 percent; Kravchuk, 39.09 
percent; Kuchma, 18 percent; Lanovyy, 12.66 percent; Moroz, 
20.88 percent; Plyushch, 1.67 percent; and Talanchuk, 0.55 
percent. 
  Chernigov oblast: Babych, 1.86 percent; Kravchuk, 20.91 
percent; Kuchma, 45.53 percent; Lanovyy, 7.56 percent; Moroz, 
15.08 percent; Plyushch, 3.2 percent; and Talanchuk, 0.49 
