<F P=100> National Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Election Commission Postpones Poll Result Briefing </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Election Commission Postpones Poll Result Briefing </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2706192894 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1751 GMT 27 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2706192894 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow INTERFAX </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Ukrainian Central Election Commission tonight 
announced a postponement of the news conference on the 
preliminary results of the presidential elections earlier 
scheduled for 1100 on 28 June. 
  The commission told INTERFAX-Ukraine that the large volume 
of 
information to be processed and the slow pace of its 
transmission made the summing up of results in such a short 
period of time impossible. 
  The commission said that general information on the results 
of the Ukrainian presidential elections divulged by the media 
had nothing to do with the official sources. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

