<H3> <TI>   Cabinet Creates Prime Minister's Secretariat </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Cabinet Creates Prime Minister's Secretariat </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU2806131294 Kiev URYADOVYY KURYER in Ukrainian 25 Jun 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> AU2806131294 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev URYADOVYY KURYER </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Ukraine's Cabinet of Ministers Decree No. 427 on Creating </F>
the Secretariat of Ukraine's Prime Minister" issued on 16 June; 
place not given] 
  [Text] Ukraine's Cabinet of Ministers decrees as follows: 
  1. To create within the apparatus of Ukraine's Cabinet of 
Ministers the Secretariat of Ukraine's Prime Minister, having 
abolished Ukraine's Prime Minister's Office. 
  2. To appoint Kasyan, Vasyl Vasylyovych as head of the 
Secretariat of Ukraine's Prime Minister and confer upon him 
category three of state official. 
  [Signed] Ukraine's Prime Minister V. Masol 
  [Signed] Minister of Ukraine's Cabinet of Ministers I. 
Dotsenko 

</TEXT>

